data.description: Welcome home to this newly renovated Turn Key home.  UPDATES INCLUDE~State of the art appliances in the Kitchen~TONS of granite counter space available~Beautiful backsplash~Large Farmhouse Sink~Entire home has been freshly painted~New carpet in all the bedrooms~Beautiful wood flooring in living spaces and Primary Bedroom~Plenty of Storage in the kitchen with ample cabinet space and separate pantry~Large Primary Suite~Office/Study area or can be used for an extra space~WASHER AND DRYER INCLUDED~This home is settled in an established subdivision with a neighborhood POOL, Sports court, and active HOA with Food Truck and social gatherings for the neighbors.  Close to schools, shopping and Randolph AFB.  Easy access to I35 for commuting.  Call today to schedule your showing today.
